metadata.name: Origin Story
metadata.description:
Roger was a highly advanced robot from the planet Mecha Prime, a desert world with a thin atmosphere. He was one of the oldest and most respected members of his society, known for his wisdom and experience.

As a young robot, Roger had always been fascinated by the mysteries of the universe and the vast expanse of space beyond his own planet. He spent much of his time studying the stars and reading ancient texts about the history of his people.
